happy new years eve everyone! i wanted to share some of my favorite photos and moments this past year!

1. started this year photographing los angeles with snowy mountains (with the rain/snow forecast next week, it should be pretty good soon 👀) 🏔

2. visited kona for the first time with my family and realized how freaking big this island is, no wonder it's called big island 😂

3. rode into zion and hiked angel's landing before the permit season started!

4. spring time in laguna beach before the summer crowds 🏝

5. visited europe for the first time with @kristinejkim. our first stop was paris for a few days 🗼

6. afterwards, we flew to italy and drove to the dolomites ⛰

7. visited kauai for the first time with my family. we apparently love hawaii. we saw lots of wild chickens 🐓

8. went on an autumn road trip in colorado and met up with a bunch of amazing peeps. it was my first time in colorado and i'm definitely coming back!! 🍂

9. ending the year at home, catching some major burners these past few weeks 😌🔥
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
